, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God! O God! O God! O God! O God! O God! O God! To You belong the most Beautiful Names the highest examples, the Magnificence, the Favors and the Blessings. I ask You by Your Name In the Name of God, Most Compassionate, Most Merciful that if it is destined by You to send down the angels and the Holy Spirit on this night for every affair of wisdom.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ يَا اللهُ لَكَ الْاَسْمَاۗءُ الْحُسْنٰى وَالْاَمْثَالُ الْعُلْيَا وَالْكِبْرِيَاۗءُ وَالْآلَاءُ وَالنَّعْمَاۗءُ اَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ اِنْ كُنْتَ قَضَيْتَ فِيْ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةِ تَنَزُّلَ الْمَلَائِكَةِ وَالرُّوْحِ مِنْ كُلِّ اَمْرٍ حَكِيْمٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "Ara