. Please relieve me from all my sorrow and sadness. Do not subject me to the enemy’s ridicule. And on the Night of Destiny give me success better than anyone has seen, and give me success as You gave Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) success. Give me peace and do such and such things (mention your needs…) for me at this very hour.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَارْزُقْنِي الْعِفَّةَ فِيْ بَطْنِيْ وَفَرْجِيْ وَفَرِّجْ عَنِّيْ كُلَّ هَمٍّ وَغَمٍّ وَلَا تُشْمِتْ بِيْ عَدُوِّيْ وَ وَفِّقْ لِي لَيْلَةَ الْقَدْرِ عَلٰى اَفْضَلِ مَا رَآهَا اَحَدٌ وَ وَفِّقْنِيْ لِمَا وَفَّقْتَ لَهٗ مُحَمَّدًا وَآلَ مُحَمَّدٍ عَلَيْهِ وَعَلَيْهِمْ سَلَامُكَ وَافْعَلْ بِيْ كَذَا وَكَذَا السَّاعَةَ السَّاعَةَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBl